# Subscription & Payment System - Implementation Walkthrough

Complete Razorpay-based subscription system for upgrading users from FREE to PREMIUM plan.

## Architecture Overview

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant F as Frontend
    participant B as Backend
    participant R as Razorpay
    participant D as Database

    U->>F: Click Upgrade
    F->>B: POST /subscription/create-order
    B->>R: Create Order
    R-->>B: Order ID
    B->>D: Save Payment (PENDING)
    B-->>F: Order details
    F->>R: Open Checkout
    U->>R: Complete Payment
    R-->>F: Payment response
    F->>B: POST /subscription/verify
    B->>B: Verify signature
    B->>D: Update Payment (SUCCESS)
    B->>D: Activate Subscription
    B-->>F: Success
    R->>B: Webhook (backup)
```

---

