## API Endpoints

| Method | Endpoint | Auth | Description |
|--------|----------|------|-------------|
| `POST` | `/v1/subscription/create-order` | ✅ | Create Razorpay order |
| `POST` | `/v1/subscription/verify` | ✅ | Verify payment after checkout |
| `POST` | `/v1/subscription/webhook` | ❌* | Handle Razorpay webhooks |
| `GET` | `/v1/subscription/status` | ✅ | Get subscription status |
| `GET` | `/v1/subscription/payments` | ✅ | Get payment history |

*Webhook is public but signature-verified using Razorpay API secret

---

## Setup Instructions

### 1. Environment Variables

**Backend** ([apps/http-backend/.env](file:///c:/Projects/excalidraw-app/apps/http-backend/.env)):
```env
RAZORPAY_KEY_ID=rzp_test_xxxxxxxxxxxxx
RAZORPAY_KEY_SECRET=your-razorpay-key-secret
```

**Frontend** ([apps/excalidraw-frontend/.env](file:///c:/Projects/excalidraw-app/apps/excalidraw-frontend/.env)):
```env
NEXT_PUBLIC_RAZORPAY_KEY_ID=rzp_test_xxxxxxxxxxxxx
```

### 2. Run Migration

```bash
cd packages/db
npx prisma migrate dev
```

### 3. Configure Razorpay Webhook (Optional)

1. Go to [Razorpay Dashboard](https://dashboard.razorpay.com/app/webhooks)
2. Add webhook URL: `https://your-domain.com/v1/subscription/webhook`
3. Select events: `payment.captured`, `payment.failed`

> [!NOTE]
> Webhook is a backup mechanism. Primary verification happens client-side after checkout.

---

## User Flow Summary

| Plan | Canvas Limit | Visibility | Edit Access |
|------|-------------|------------|-------------|
| FREE | 2 | All owned | ✅ Full |
| PREMIUM | 10 | All owned | ✅ Full |
| EXPIRED | 2 (visible) | 2 most recent | ❌ Read-only |
